  <description>
    The display tag library is an open source suite of custom tags that provide high level web presentation patterns
    (like tables, tabs, templates, inspectors, trees, etc...) which will work in a MVC model, and provide a significant
    amount of functionality while still being simple and straight-forward to use.
  </description>
